Hello dear CURIOS Weltenverbesserer !

This category goes unhinged as the File name already suggests.

Please be aware that here we share and talk though experiments, bold predictions and taboo topics which are seen as Harsh in the Public eye.

I urge you to not take everything to heart, even if some things seem though,rough and creates chuff.
Feel free to download the provided data, and keep building and upload it back with your changes to create diversity, 
Like vol.2 of the Topic such and such.(First one gets to choose the Layout of the Episodes)

Its also suggestable to describe your titles well, so the reader can be aware what field s/he is entering.

Also bear in mind, some things are recorded through speech, i urge you to overlook wording, grammar, and personal ticks 
to keep it interesting and avoid being annoyed. 

Focus rather on the answers then the correctness of the question.

All the fun!!
